translations: <俚>胆小鬼；<俚>阴茎（weenie 的复数）

sentences.sentence: Just the thought of it made me so happy inside (his beanie weenies turned out great!)
sentences.translation: 只是这个想法就让我的内心兴奋不已。

sentences.sentence: This incident is just an example of you press weenies trying to fire up some kind of controversy-and I'm not going to be a part of it.
sentences.translation: 这件事件就是由吹毛求疵引起一场论战的范例——我不会去做那样的事情。
